uing building up their mass\nuntil z=0. Overall, these results indicate that lopsidedness in present-day\ndisk galaxies is connected to the specific evolutionary histories of the\ngalaxies that shaped their distinct internal properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2023 17:59:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-08"}
