tion, the examination of pressures reveals that the total pressures are\ncomparable through a switchback, confirming switchbacks are pressure-balanced\nstructures. These characteristics could further our understanding of ion\nheating, electron scattering, and the structure of switchbacks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2023 20:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-09"}
