puter networks, data\ncommunication, and imaging systems with the potential to revolutionize on-chip\nlogic and optoelectronic integration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2023 13:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-09"}
